      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/kotak-shares-soar-on-analyst-upgrades-as-asset-quality-holds-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科塔克马辛德拉银行有限公司 (Kotak Mahindra Bank Ltd.) 股价上涨，因该银行报告第三季度新增不良贷款减少，引发分析师上调评级。]]></description>
